@WHOWPRO @WHOSEARO @WHO_Europe @pahowho @WHOEMRO @WHOAFRO Q: Are there any specific medicines to prevent or treat the new #coronavirus (2019-nCoV)?
A: To date, there is no specific medicine recommended to prevent or treat the virus.
WHO is helping to accelerate research and development efforts with a range of partners. https://t.co/VyFEUfGWgM
